{
  "stem": "7683.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Selma, all the things she saw-- friends she saw dead, and she made me more scary as it was.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we ran till-- and we tried already, because I wanted to come someplace.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe some farmer will want to keep me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we kept asking people if  they want to keep us for money.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We told them-- well, surely mostly did not-- did not.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we had-- sometimes we could leave during the day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We tried at night, during the day being hidden in someplace.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we couldn't always find a farmer or the place where to hide out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we were sometimes just in the field.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one time, we were hiding in a-- in a-- hoy--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Haystack.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Haystack.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then some kids were playing there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they came on the haystack and saw us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it was very dangerous.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the middle of the day, we had to go expose us and go in-- go in somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one fact I remember, one thing, we were two farmers, one with wagons.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe Selma told it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and I spoke Polish, so they-- oh, they said they will take us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But they didn't know that I speak Polish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So while we are on the wagon, I on one and she on the other, and they say, oh, the Jews, we will take them, and we do things like that.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I say to Selma, jump.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we jump right away on these wagons, and we ran away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they didn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had more cases like that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was really hard because sometimes we will ask people for water, wouldn't give us nothing-- food, no, not at all.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
